values:
My sister starts school tomorrow. 

I am no longer jealous that she gets to stay home cuz I will be home more then her. 

MUHAHAH! 

<3

So boys suck. 

Parents suck.

Little sisters suck. 

Friends suck. 

BAH. 

If I was still in my manic depressive state I would be cutting myself today. 

My dad was like "Just let her scream it makes her feel better" @ dinner in one of his sarcastic jerk tones...

"Well dad yes, it does make me feel better, it's either screaming or I start cutting myself again...whatever you want though"

That shut him up. 

He needs anger managment and to see a therpist. 

SHIT THE WHOLE FUCKING FAMILY DOES. 

I am going insane...I should have stayed in the "O.C."

It has got to be better then this. 

I am done bitching. 

x o x o

I hate ex-boyfriends. 

Why can't they just let you be nice to them...why they gotta be an ass. 

Maybe it's just my mexican ex-boyfriends. 

I hate mexican men.
 
Not really. 

BUT FUCK MAN.
Grandma and Mimi left for Michigan...I wanted them to stay longer...hell I want them to stay forever. I wish they would. </3
Your Love Keeps Me Going At Night. </3
Grandma and Mimi are here!! I am so excited!! <33 I love them.

I love waking up to an empty house. 

No. 

Strike that. 

<s>I love waking up to an empty house.</s>

I hate it. And without a note...well. THAT MAKES MY DAY!
